    public class GridPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.io.Serializable
    Created by Ryan on 4/8/2015 This class represents the grid that will graphically display all cell activity. The gameState which is a grid of booleans representing what cells are alive and dead will be serialized.
